text: L'Orée-d'ÉcouvesArrêté préfectoral 10 July 2018 (rectification) is a commune in the Orne department in north-western France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Livaie (the seat), Fontenai- les-Louvets, Longuenoë and Saint-Didier-sous-Écouves.Arrêté préfectoral 10 July 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Orne department ==References== Category:Communes of Orne Category:States and territories established in 2019
title: L'Orée-d'Écouves
